These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, nurse, paramedic, pilot, security-guard
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bluemaster, dunhill, game, aristoff, oliveros
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
 4. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the nurse##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
 6. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the security-guard##7
 7. the lawyer is not to the left of the dunhill-smoker##8
 8. the pilot is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pilot##3
10. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the paramedic##8
11. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
12. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
13. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
14. the security-guard is somewhere between the bluemaster-smoker and the nurse##7
15. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
16. the pilot is not the game-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | paramedic | manager | lawyer | pilot | security-guard | nurse |
| Cigar   | old-henry | dunhill    | bluemaster  | aristoff  | game            | oliveros  |

