.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, dog, horse, bird, frog
 1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the polish and the owner of the dog##7
12. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
13. the spanish is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the frog##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the american##7
16. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
17. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
18. the polish is the owner of the rat##1
19. the owner of the dog is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | polish   | british | spanish    | canadian      | argentine | american |
| Pet         | rat | bird  | chinchilla | frog | dog   | horse  |

