 4. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
10. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who likes red##7
13. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
14. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
