 4. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person driving the bike##7
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the car and the person driving the helicopter##2
 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the owner of the horse is not the person driving the skateboard##6
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Transport   | bike | motorbike | helicopter  | bus     | car | skateboard |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

