.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-18::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, pony, lizard, bird, chinchilla, frog
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cauliflower, cranberry, garlic, lime, potato
 1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 2. the person eating lime is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person eating cauliflower##7
 3. the person eating lime is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
 5. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
 7. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
 9. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
10. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
12. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
13. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
14. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
15. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
16. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
17. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
